366
00:22:37,067 --> 00:22:37,692
Yes sir.

367
00:22:37,775 --> 00:22:39,233
I apologize for that.

368
00:22:39,317 --> 00:22:42,192
Honestly...

369
00:22:42,275 --> 00:22:43,275
Yes, sir.

370
00:22:43,358 --> 00:22:45,108
You're behaving
more like a man, now.

371
00:22:45,192 --> 00:22:46,192
Sir?

