to me you're more
important than that.

395
00:24:19,733 --> 00:24:23,358
And, if something ever
happens I'll be there for you

396
00:24:23,442 --> 00:24:25,275
Please remember that

397
00:24:27,317 --> 00:24:28,692
Forgive me, I'm sorry
about that, okay?

